{"tid":1612901,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"CNN：抗爭者想攪和中國大日子 他們成功了","createTime":"2019-10-02T11:32:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T12:22:52.000Z","uid":68738,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a2401e7bc6613b0e19d47105e9f7b5f02739714f","tid":1612901,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:32:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191002/large/1569988286_9464.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191002%2Flarge%2F1569988286_9464.jpg&h=872f93b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多個外國主流傳媒都認為，本港的抗爭者成功在10月1日搶走國際社會對中國慶祝建政70周年的關注，特別是警方向示威者轟實彈的行為，令對香港連日示威興趣漸減的國際傳媒，再次聚焦在港人抗爭上。<br />\n<br />\n美國有線新聞網絡（CNN）的評論以「香港示威者發動攪和中國的大日子，他們成功了」為題，評論員格里菲斯（James Griffiths）指，天安門大搞萬人聯歡晚會展示歌舞昇平，香港卻是一片混亂，多區都有示威抗爭。他指中國國家主席習近平在周二早上的閱兵式吸引到世界注目，「但當慶祝活動在傍晚繼續時，全球都在關注香港情況，成為習近平一方最大的一根刺」。<br />\n<br />\n評論指，香港有約6,000名警員執勤，都無法平息動盪，因為抗爭者是遍佈全港各地，「是一名警員的行為令北京慶祝活動被搶走焦點&hellip;&hellip;在荃灣的衝突中，一名警員向示威者轟實彈，是警方在17周的示威中首次使用致命武力。這令全球傳媒再次聚焦香港局勢」。<br />\n<br />\n格里菲斯寫道：「負責周二傍晚表演的官員們&mdash;&mdash;這是一場規模與組織都令人驚艷的演出&mdash;&mdash;將會因他們和國家的重要時刻，被中國其中一個時常希望與國家沒關係的地方搶走而感憤怒。香港已破壞中國的慶祝活動，動盪亦正加劇並變得暴力，這可能讓北京更敢於以強硬手段應對」。<br />\n<br />\n而《紐約時報》以編輯部之名，發表題為「北京的歡呼聲無法淹過香港示威者」的評論，指本港抗爭者在昨天顯然對北京的活動沒有興趣，「相反他們把握這機會，搶過對北京表演的焦點，展示對抗中共間接干預香港自治地位的態度」。<br />\n<br />\n評論指：「以冷戰時代的用語來說，自由世界（free world）應與港人並肩，一同對抗中國共產黨，並向北京發出逼切訊息，說明當緊張局勢上升到臨界點，中方若有以武力鎮壓示威的意圖，將惹來猛烈迴響」。<br />\n<br />\n文中又指，習近平認為在70周年慶祝中不談及香港問題是恰當，而美國總統特朗普亦糾纏於與習近平愛恨交纏的關係中，如稱讚對方為人但又加徵關稅，「他（特朗普）可能視香港及其願景是令人遺憾地失焦，但不能避免國會或美國盟友會發聲」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191002/60107305?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191002%2F60107305%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2BmpKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=4be8f1ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191002%2F60107305%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=7ff05232\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191002/60107305?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"ef4d2fee95e7c2e1ed68300cdd446ee6c4749c4e","tid":1612901,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:33:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4eaf05f2d778a0088522c4431aee5f2e0bb7c1c","tid":1612901,"uid":76835,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:36:45.000Z","msg":"搶到foc但無左好多手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f9981d3c75598273406ea5930b12ede0e960c2","tid":1612901,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4eaf05f2d778a0088522c4431aee5f2e0bb7c1c","tid":1612901,"uid":76835,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:36:45.000Z","msg":"搶到foc但無左好多手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:37:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d244ef9187b8dbef9feac65174329c9fe38feb15","tid":1612901,"uid":24634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eeb990ae2a533dd98fd26ffcc2bf3577e5bfe5d","tid":1612901,"uid":78769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:58:40.000Z","msg":"算啦，中共玩國內圍爐一樣得。中國人係唔會覺得受影響，但中共領導階層唔係。"},{"pid":"be4e2993cffaa1892f4cb00165e9a93557b3f994","tid":1612901,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:22:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">十一假期connect埋全中國人執行國歌</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其實我地先係最愛國嗰個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1612478\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1612478</a></span>"}]}